is that Father is
going to be married.

2081
02:01:57,890 --> 02:01:59,118
Married?

2082
02:01:59,192 --> 02:02:01,456
Yes, to Baroness
Schraeder.

2083
02:02:08,034 --> 02:02:09,968
Oh, I see.

2084
02:02:12,538 --> 02:02:13,971
Oh, Father, look!

2085
02:02:14,040 --> 02:02:18,500
Fraulein Maria's
come back from the abbey!

2086
02:02:20,046 --> 02:02:21,707
Good evening, Captain.

2087
02:02:23,049 --> 02:02:24,482
Good evening.

2088
02:02:26,552 --> 02:02:28,042
All right,
everyone inside.

2089
02:02:28,121 --> 02:02:29,986
Go and get your dinner.

2090
02:02:30,056 --> 02:02:31,489
Dinner!

2091
02:02:39,065 --> 02:02:42,000
You left without
saying good-bye,

2092
02:02:42,068 --> 02:02:44,764
even to the children.

2093
02:02:44,837 --> 02:02:47,362
Well, it was wrong
of me. Forgive me.

2094
02:02:47,440 --> 02:02:49,931
Why did you?

2095
02:02:50,009 --> 02:02:51,601
Please don't ask me.

2096
02:02:51,677 --> 02:02:53,611
Anyway, the reason
no longer exists.

2097
02:02:53,679 --> 02:02:57,080
Fraulein Maria.
You've returned.

2098
02:02:58,584 --> 02:03:00,916
Isn't it wonderful,
Georg?

2099
02:03:03,956 --> 02:03:06,049
May I wish you
every happiness, baroness,

2100
02:03:06,125 --> 02:03:07,319
and you, too, Captain.

2101
02:03:07,393 --> 02:03:09,020
The children tell me
you're to be married.

2102
02:03:09,095 --> 02:03:10,756
Thank you, my dear.

2103
02:03:12,798 --> 02:03:15,733
You are back
to, uh, stay?

2104
02:03:17,270 --> 02:03:19,795
Only until arrangements

2105
02:03:19,872 --> 02:03:21,840
can be made for
another governess.

2106
02:04:17,263 --> 02:04:18,958
There you are!

2107
02:04:32,712 --> 02:04:35,146
I really must
speak to Cook

2108
02:04:35,214 --> 02:04:36,738
about the wiener
schnitzel.

2109
02:04:36,816 --> 02:04:39,444
It is entirely too delicious
for my figure.

2110
02:04:39,518 --> 02:04:41,782
And it makes you
much too quiet

2111
02:04:41,854 --> 02:04:44,084
at the dinner table,

2112
02:04:44,156 --> 02:04:46,090
or was it the wine?

2113
02:04:46,158 --> 02:04:47,557
Oh, undoubtedly
the wine.

2114
02:04:47,627 --> 02:04:51,256
You have no idea what kind
of trouble I'm having

2115
