Maria.

2264
02:14:57,104 --> 02:15:00,540
Is there anyone
I should go to

2265
02:15:00,607 --> 02:15:03,542
to ask permission
to marry you?

2266
02:15:05,112 --> 02:15:07,546
Well, why don't
we ask--

2267
